Singaporeans snap up free Hong Kong air tickets within the hour02 Mar 2023 17:25MANY people in Singapore were left disappointed on Thursday (Mar 2) after 12 500 free air tickets to Hong Kong were snapped up in short order.The tickets  being given away by Cathay Pacific Airway  were available from midday local time. Within 60 minutes  the website had reverted to a message saying all tickets had already been awarded  with winners to be announced on March 20.
